query:
SELECT 
  DATE_FORMAT(s.saleDate, '%Y-%m') as mes,
  SUM(s.quantity) as total_quantidade
FROM sales s
JOIN products p ON s.productId = p.id
WHERE p.code = '36543'
  AND s.saleDate >= '2025-09-01'
  AND s.saleDate < '2025-10-01'
GROUP BY mes
